## Limitations

This report is based on available data and sources up to October 2023. The complexity of Brexit means that motivations and impacts are subject to interpretation and ongoing analysis. Additionally, the political landscape continues to evolve, potentially altering the long-term effects of Brexit. Some sources may have inherent biases, and the full impact of Brexit is still emerging, which may not be fully captured in this report.